1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 21=

4
00:01:08,580 --> 00:01:09,359
What are you doing?

5
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:17,840
Your Majesty.

6
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:19,959
What's been wrong with you lately?

7
00:01:20,260 --> 00:01:21,810
You've been avoiding me this whole time.

8
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:24,400
I still have matters
to handle in my palace.

9
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,560
I'll take my leave first.

10
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:42,200
What were you two
talking about just now?

11
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,940
Why doesn't Your Majesty
ask Miss Shen instead?

12
00:01:44,959 --> 00:01:46,359
I still need to visit the Empress.

13
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:47,510
I'll take my leave.

14
00:01:54,719 --> 00:01:56,480
Go ask Handan about it.

15
00:01:58,040 --> 00:02:00,400
Find out what
Shen Zhinian is upset about.

16
00:02:00,879 --> 00:02:02,079
Yes.

17
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:05,959
Your Majesty,

18
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,239
I went to Tinglan Palace,

19
00:02:07,260 --> 00:02:08,879
but Lady Shen and Handan were both gone.

20
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,840
Why is she suddenly angry with me?

21
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:15,080
What did I do yesterday to upset her?

22
00:02:15,639 --> 00:02:17,479
Why not go comfort her, Your Majesty?

23
00:02:19,439 --> 00:02:20,280
How?

24
00:02:20,290 --> 00:02:21,759
Just do what Lady Shen usually does.

25
00:02:21,950 --> 00:02:23,990
Didn't you say
she's the best at comforting people?

26
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,800
Send someone to check Tinglan Palace.

27
00:02:26,810 --> 00:02:28,740
The moment she returns,
report to me immediately.

28
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:29,240
Yes.

29
00:02:30,639 --> 00:02:31,840
Once we find her grandfather,

30
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,120
give her this death-exemption medal.

31
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,039
Where's the medal?

32
00:02:42,500 --> 00:02:43,840
If Young Lady
wanted to avoid His Majesty,

33
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,590
there was no need
to crawl through a dog hole.

34
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,120
His men are guarding outside.

35
00:02:47,319 --> 00:02:48,360
I don't want to see him.

36
00:02:48,370 --> 00:02:49,960
His Majesty already gave you
the death-exemption medal,

37
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,199
and now he wants it back.

38
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,919
Isn't that bullying you?

39
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:54,140
He even deceived your grandfather.

40
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:56,390
Men really are like venomous snakes
once they turn heartless.

41
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,000
Your Majesty.

42
00:02:59,159 --> 00:02:59,719
Leave us.

43
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:00,599
Yes.

44
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,719
About the death-exemption medal,

45
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,680
listen to my explanation first.

46
00:03:10,690 --> 00:03:12,330
There's no need to explain,
Your Majesty.

47
00:03:12,599 --> 00:03:14,120
You've never trusted me.

48
00:03:14,130 --> 00:03:16,039
And now you want
to use my grandfather's family

49
00:03:16,039 --> 00:03:16,790
to keep me under control.

50
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,560
That's not true.

51
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:18,759
Of course not.

52
00:03:18,860 --> 00:03:20,319
I was the one who judged a gentleman

53
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:21,700
with the heart of a petty person.

54
00:03:21,919 --> 00:03:22,759
I'll take my leave.

55
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,590
Your grandfather's
disappearance was an accident.

56
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:27,400
After hearing you mention them,

57
00:03:27,410 --> 00:03:29,390
I only wanted to bring them
to the capital so you could reunite.

58
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,520
As for the death-exemption medal,

59
00:03:32,599 --> 00:03:34,360
I forgot to withdraw the decree.

60
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,280
Since I already granted it,

61
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,759
why would I take it back?

62
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:42,639
I remember every word Your Majesty said,

63
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:44,080
and I believed all of it.

64
00:03:44,090 --> 00:03:46,510
But there are always so many things
you keep hidden from me.

65
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:49,680
(Nangong Xuanyu.)

66
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,879
(Have you truly never trusted me?)

67
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:55,240
(Shen Zhinian.)

68
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,639
(What will it take for you to trust me?)

69
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,240
Your Majesty,

70
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,199
you're just

71
00:04:06,439 --> 00:04:07,400
coming back like this?

72
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,879
Tonight is the full moon.

73
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:12,439
Do you expect me
to lose control in front of her?

74
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,680
I'll go prepare the water.

75
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,759
Come back.

76
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,879
She even managed
to get into my secret chamber.

77
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:19,759
I don't know whether to call
her bold or reckless.

78
00:04:20,199 --> 00:04:21,160
And all of you,

79
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,920
with so many eyes watching,

80
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,580
yet none of you noticed
someone sneaking in.

81
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,199
Your Majesty,

82
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,920
I have an idea

83
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:31,160
to calm Lady Shen down.

84
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,480
Speak.

85
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,800
Women are soft hearted
and easily sympathize with others.

86
00:04:35,810 --> 00:04:37,720
If Lady Shen sees
how much Your Majesty suffers

87
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,800
when the poison flares up,

88
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:40,160
she'll surely soften up

89
00:04:40,319 --> 00:04:41,759
and stop blaming you.

90
00:04:42,170 --> 00:04:44,480
I don't make a habit
of acting pitiful in front of women.

91
00:04:45,319 --> 00:04:47,040
Only useless men do that.

92
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,759
I clearly tied it shut.

93
00:05:04,759 --> 00:05:05,839
How did you get in?

94
00:05:13,199 --> 00:05:14,399
Why are you burning up?

95
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:15,920
Are you sick?

96
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,480
Let go of me.

97
00:05:22,959 --> 00:05:24,040
Nangong Xuanyu,

98
00:05:24,519 --> 00:05:25,560
let go of me!

99
00:05:28,260 --> 00:05:29,279
You are the Son of Heaven.

100
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:30,920
Please show some restraint.

101
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,160
Shen Zhinian,

102
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,959
don't leave me.

103
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:42,620
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

104
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:46,580
♪If we don't meet♪

105
00:05:46,580 --> 00:05:49,900
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

106
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,199
Forgive me, Lady Shen.

107
00:05:53,199 --> 00:05:55,150
Whenever there's a full moon,
His Majesty's poison flares up.

108
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:57,399
At times like this,
he must avoid intimacy with women.

109
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,360
You mean

110
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,040
he's poisoned?

111
00:06:02,650 --> 00:06:03,720
After His Majesty was born,

112
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,950
the late Emperor
personally forced poison into him.

113
00:06:06,439 --> 00:06:09,480
As he grew older, the poison attacks
became worse and worse.

114
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,600
Every full moon,

115
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:11,680
it's like being trapped

116
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,780
between unbearable
freezing cold and scorching heat.

117
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,079
His muscles and bones

118
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:16,990
feel as if they're
being torn apart piece by piece.

119
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,879
What about the antidote?

120
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:20,319
While the late Dowager Consort
was still alive,

121
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:21,600
she did obtain the antidote.

122
00:06:21,730 --> 00:06:24,600
But unfortunately, before the antidote
could be delivered to His Majesty,

123
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,519
the late Dowager Consort passed away,

124
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,839
and the medicine disappeared with her.

125
00:06:29,879 --> 00:06:30,360
Then

126
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,839
go look for it now.

127
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,990
It can no longer be found.

128
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,680
That medicine was made
by the late Dowager Consort

129
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:36,390
using her own heart's
blood as the catalyst.

130
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,460
The bond between mother and child.

131
00:06:38,570 --> 00:06:40,319
There was only ever
one pill in this world.

132
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:47,959
Take him back.

133
00:06:49,010 --> 00:06:51,240
Could My Ladyship please help
care for His Majesty tonight?

134
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:56,820
♪Wanting to fold my heart
into a paper kite♪

135
00:06:56,820 --> 00:07:03,420
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

136
00:07:10,300 --> 00:07:11,990
Because of the poison
in His Majesty's body,

137
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,680
his wounds are always slow to heal.

138
00:07:14,210 --> 00:07:16,199
But the path to the throne
is filled with danger.

139
00:07:17,079 --> 00:07:17,839
His injuries

140
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,360
have never truly healed.

141
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:21,560
(His injuries are this severe,)

142
00:07:21,570 --> 00:07:23,290
(and he still runs around
everywhere every day.)

143
00:07:23,300 --> 00:07:24,850
(Why doesn't the pain kill you already?)

144
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,480
Serves you right for taking my medal.

145
00:07:28,010 --> 00:07:29,920
Serves you right
for taking my grandfather's family away

146
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,759
without telling me.

147
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,880
Serves you right
for losing my grandfather.

148
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:33,800
Tyrant.

149
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,480
Cold blooded.

150
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,319
Cruel.

151
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,800
That feels good.

152
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,639
Your Majesty.

153
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:50,920
That feels good.

154
00:08:08,399 --> 00:08:09,879
What's going on?

155
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,240
I didn't sleep at all last night,

156
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,279
and I had to attend
morning greetings first thing today.

157
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:24,720
I'm exhausted.

158
00:08:27,790 --> 00:08:29,399
Lord Jiang, do you need something again?

159
00:08:29,839 --> 00:08:30,920
My father's case

160
00:08:30,930 --> 00:08:32,900
has already been handed over
to the Court of Judicial Review.

161
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:35,440
For a while,
I won't be entering the palace again.

162
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,970
But I still can't stop worrying
about the Empress.

163
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,159
I'd like to trouble Lady Shen

164
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:40,520
to look after Her Highness for me.

165
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:44,200
If the Empress ever needs me,

166
00:08:44,639 --> 00:08:45,600
I'll do everything I can.

167
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,639
Thank you.

168
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,720
After this, I'll resign

169
00:08:50,090 --> 00:08:51,279
and travel through the south.

170
00:08:57,060 --> 00:08:58,950
Lord Jiang was never meant
to be confined by court life.

171
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,550
I'm sure everything
will go smoothly for you.

172
00:09:09,759 --> 00:09:11,320
She's really difficult to deal with,

173
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,399
prickly from head to toe.

174
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:16,250
No wonder she's such
a perfect match for Nangong Xuanyu.

175
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:17,720
Then what do we do now?

176
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,399
Since that's the case,

177
00:09:23,399 --> 00:09:26,600
doesn't Nangong Xuanyu
want to find the Prince of Jin?

178
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:29,000
Release Song Yuqing.

179
00:09:35,420 --> 00:09:37,279
Why is Your Majesty
holding my imperial decree?

180
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:38,919
Are you going back on your word again?

181
00:09:48,399 --> 00:09:49,960
About the death-exemption medal,

182
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:51,840
I wasn't the one
who ordered it intercepted.

183
00:09:51,919 --> 00:09:52,799
And your grandfather

184
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:55,080
wasn't abducted on my orders either.

185
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:56,890
I've already explained everything.

186
00:09:57,159 --> 00:09:58,440
Why won't you believe me?

187
00:10:00,759 --> 00:10:01,879
You claim to value fairness,

188
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,519
but where is that fairness?

189
00:10:04,159 --> 00:10:05,919
You're the one who drew me in first.

190
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:08,720
Fine.

191
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,660
You want to talk about fairness, right?

192
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,390
Then let me spell it out for you.

193
00:10:12,919 --> 00:10:14,600
The first time
we met in the Cold Palace,

194
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,480
weren't you trying
to push me into the lake?

195
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:19,790
At Shanglin Garden,
when I was nearly strangled to death,

196
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,720
didn't you just stand there and watch?

197
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,290
When I was in the Cold Palace,

198
00:10:23,559 --> 00:10:25,440
you ignored me completely.

199
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:27,120
If Handan hadn't been poisoned first,

200
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:28,840
the one in trouble would've been me.

201
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,879
Was that fair to me?

202
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:34,679
You're arrogant, and suspicious by nature.

203
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,039
You don't actually think
I really like you, do you?

204
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:44,320
You said you liked me
just to deceive me.

205
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,159
Shen Zhinian,

206
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:50,960
that's deceiving the Emperor.

207
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:51,879
I wouldn't dare.

208
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,590
What is there that you wouldn't dare do?

209
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:54,759
Last night,

210
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:56,200
you poked at my wound

211
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,039
six times in a row.

212
00:11:01,039 --> 00:11:02,559
You were counting?

213
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:07,919
Wait,

214
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,879
you were conscious last night?

215
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,720
How much did you hear?

216
00:11:15,639 --> 00:11:16,480
Everything.

217
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:19,639
Everything?

218
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,360
Shen Zhinian,

219
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:24,039
I feel pain too.

220
00:11:24,559 --> 00:11:27,080
My chest is practically
full of holes from your poking.

221
00:11:29,210 --> 00:11:31,190
That was because
Your Majesty was already injured.

222
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,399
I don't care.

223
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,500
You still have to take responsibility.

224
00:11:35,519 --> 00:11:37,039
Why are you acting shamelessly?

225
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,440
And if I refuse?

226
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,320
What will you do?

227
00:11:39,330 --> 00:11:40,679
Exterminate my whole clan again?

228
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:43,279
Can you stop throwing accusations at me?

229
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:45,240
I've never slaughtered innocent people.

230
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:05,799
Sorry.

231
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:07,919
It's all my fault.

232
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:09,840
(He actually apologized?)

233
00:12:09,919 --> 00:12:10,639
Your Majesty,

234
00:12:10,679 --> 00:12:11,480
good news.

235
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,360
Your Majesty,

236
00:12:14,519 --> 00:12:15,440
we found them.

237
00:12:16,919 --> 00:12:17,679
Yiqing.

238
00:12:18,279 --> 00:12:19,000
Bao'er.

239
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,480
Zhinian.

240
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,279
Aunt.

241
00:12:21,919 --> 00:12:22,759
Are you alright?

242
00:12:23,799 --> 00:12:26,000
I am He Yiqing. Greetings, Your Majesty.

243
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:26,879
Rise.

244
00:12:28,039 --> 00:12:29,200
What exactly happened?

245
00:12:29,399 --> 00:12:30,879
Why did you go to Mount Nanhua?

246
00:12:31,159 --> 00:12:31,990
Where's Grandfather?

247
00:12:32,799 --> 00:12:34,000
It's a long story.

248
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:35,360
Hyah!

249
00:12:35,380 --> 00:12:36,240
Who would've thought

250
00:12:36,399 --> 00:12:38,110
that not long after
Zhinian entered the capital,

251
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:39,350
she'd already risen to Lady of Beauty

252
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:41,190
and even brought us
to the capital to reunite.

253
00:12:41,519 --> 00:12:44,000
Zhinian has finally made it
through the hard times.

254
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,399
Indeed.

255
00:12:50,559 --> 00:12:51,320
Stop for a moment.

256
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:52,100
Stop the carriage.

257
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,039
This doesn't look

258
00:12:54,039 --> 00:12:55,480
like the road to the capital.

259
00:12:55,500 --> 00:12:57,080
Lady Shen is praying at South Mountain.

260
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,420
We're taking a detour to South Mountain.

261
00:12:59,080 --> 00:12:59,519
Move.

262
00:12:59,879 --> 00:13:00,360
Hyah!

263
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:03,679
Grandfather,

264
00:13:03,679 --> 00:13:05,480
those men just now looked unfamiliar.

265
00:13:05,879 --> 00:13:07,559
They weren't
the same people from before.

266
00:13:08,879 --> 00:13:10,519
I thought so too.

267
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:16,080
Officer,

268
00:13:16,279 --> 00:13:17,360
Bao'er has an upset stomach.

269
00:13:17,650 --> 00:13:18,679
He'll go into the woods.

270
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:20,140
Wouldn't want
to offend you with the smell.

271
00:13:20,159 --> 00:13:20,679
Go on then.

272
00:13:20,680 --> 00:13:21,490
Don't wander too far.

273
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:22,679
Come on, Bao'er.

274
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,279
Why aren't they back yet?

275
00:13:31,559 --> 00:13:32,320
Did they run away?

276
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:33,759
Let's go.

277
00:13:33,759 --> 00:13:34,360
Go check.

278
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,600
Hyah!

279
00:13:45,500 --> 00:13:46,200
Stop right there!

280
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:46,879
Stop!

281
00:13:46,879 --> 00:13:47,480
Don't run!

282
00:13:47,530 --> 00:13:48,240
Stop right there!

283
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,000
Don't run!

284
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:49,440
Stop!

285
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:51,039
Along the way,

286
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,039
Bao'er and I

287
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,519
almost didn't make it back alive.

288
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,440
We finally managed to escape,

289
00:13:55,759 --> 00:13:57,480
but on the way,
we ran into another group.

290
00:13:57,500 --> 00:13:59,399
They seemed to be searching
for some kind of herb,

291
00:13:59,519 --> 00:14:01,159
shouting about burning it all down.

292
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:02,919
Luckily,

293
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,639
His Majesty's men

294
00:14:04,639 --> 00:14:05,559
found us in the end.

295
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:10,159
Eunuch Ming, take Young Master He
and Bao'er away to rest first.

296
00:14:10,639 --> 00:14:11,279
As you command.

297
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,090
We'll take our leave first.

298
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:18,240
Zhinian,

299
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:21,120
do you know
what's special about Mount Nanhua?

300
00:14:21,300 --> 00:14:23,260
The land and water
at Mount Nanhua are excellent.

301
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:25,480
Many rare medicinal herbs grow there.

302
00:14:25,670 --> 00:14:28,200
Back then, my mother often went
to Mount Nanhua to gather herbs.

303
00:14:28,639 --> 00:14:29,559
At that time,

304
00:14:29,559 --> 00:14:31,600
your mother should've already married
into the Shen family as a concubine.

305
00:14:31,610 --> 00:14:33,399
Why would she frequently
go to Mount Nanhua?

306
00:14:34,159 --> 00:14:35,679
I don't know the reason either.

307
00:14:36,399 --> 00:14:37,399
I only remember

308
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:38,759
that every month,

309
00:14:38,759 --> 00:14:41,639
my mother would leave at the same time
with someone from outside.

310
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:42,919
Unfortunately,

311
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,159
I was too young back then

312
00:14:44,430 --> 00:14:46,120
to remember what
that person looked like.

313
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,039
But I do remember

314
00:14:48,559 --> 00:14:51,039
a bright red scar on the person's wrist.

315
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,440
A scar?

316
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:58,159
Come with me.

317
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:05,919
Have you seen these women before?

318
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,240
No.

319
00:15:14,279 --> 00:15:16,399
These are portraits
of my mother and Madam Lian.

320
00:15:16,759 --> 00:15:18,559
Do you see the red scar on the wrist?

321
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:21,590
It was left behind by a secret
punishment used in the palace.

322
00:15:21,860 --> 00:15:22,960
First, the hand is cut off,

323
00:15:23,519 --> 00:15:24,440
then bone nails

324
00:15:24,559 --> 00:15:25,759
are driven into a wooden hand.

325
00:15:26,559 --> 00:15:27,879
One of Madam Lian's hands

326
00:15:27,879 --> 00:15:29,080
is made of wood.

327
00:15:31,279 --> 00:15:32,799
You mean

328
00:15:33,279 --> 00:15:36,559
the person meeting with my mother
might have been someone from the palace?

329
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:38,440
Or perhaps...

330
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,240
it was Madam Lian herself?

331
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:54,440
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

332
00:15:56,160 --> 00:16:01,400
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

333
00:16:03,040 --> 00:16:05,400
♪If we don't meet♪

334
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:08,840
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

335
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:15,560
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

336
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:22,360
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

337
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:29,040
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

338
00:16:29,560 --> 00:16:36,240
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

339
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:43,120
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

340
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:49,240
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

341
00:16:50,160 --> 00:16:56,760
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

342
00:16:56,920 --> 00:17:03,600
♪Wanting to fold my heart
into a paper kite♪

343
00:17:03,880 --> 00:17:10,320
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

